OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784895503
OL,3,COasis reunion documentary to premiere
OL,4,Cat Venice Film Festival
OL,6,FIt will premiere at Venice alongside
OL,7,Fother films including Martin
OL,8,FMcDonagh's black comedy Wild Horse
OL,9,FNine, Florian Zeller's thriller
OL,10,FBunker, Werner Herzog's Bucking
OL,11,FFastard, and Danny Boyle's Ink.
OL,13,FThe Oasis documentary was created by
OL,14,FKnight and directed by Dylan Southern
OL,15,Fand Will Lovelace.
OL,17,FSet to be released in cinemas on
OL,18,FSeptember 9, and also on Disney Plus,
OL,19,Fthe streaming service has teased that
OL,20,Fthe documentary follows the
OL,21,FGallaghers' "triumphant reunion tour".
OL,26,@}D@MOU}D@eO]
