PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784895503
OL,3,COasis reunion documentary to premiere
OL,4,Cat Venice Film Festival
OL,6,F"Oasis Live '25, one of the most
OL,7,Fanticipated rock 'n' roll comebacks of
OL,8,Four time," it says.
OL,10,F"The film is an unapologetically
OL,11,Fuplifting account of the biggest
OL,12,Fmusical event of 2025, capturing the
OL,13,Fexperience and emotions of the band
OL,14,Fand their fans across the world.
OL,16,F"The unique perspective includes
OL,17,Frehearsal, backstage, and onstage
OL,18,Faccess as well as the first joint
OL,19,Finterviews with Noel and Liam in over
OL,20,F20 years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
