PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784895503
OL,3,COasis reunion documentary to premiere
OL,4,Cat Venice Film Festival
OL,6,F"Alongside the band's sold-out world
OL,7,Ftour, the film also explores the
OL,8,Fprofound emotional impact of this
OL,9,Fphenomenal global cultural moment and
OL,10,Fwhat their music means to audiences
OL,11,Fand generations worldwide."
OL,13,FKnight said: "The Oasis world tour
OL,14,Funited generations, cultures and
OL,15,Fcountries and spoke to a broken world
OL,16,Fabout reconciliation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
