PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784895503
OL,3,COasis reunion documentary to premiere
OL,4,Cat Venice Film Festival
OL,6,F"Don't Look Back In Anger is not only
OL,7,Fyour ticket to the show ` it's a
OL,8,Fbackstage pass and a seat at the table
OL,9,Fwhen Liam and Noel sit down together
OL,10,Ffor the first time in 15 years and
OL,11,Ftell it how it is and how it was."
OL,13,FSpeaking backstage at the Brits in
OL,14,FMarch, Noel said of the documentary:
OL,15,F"I've only seen a tiny little bit of
OL,16,Fit and it's difficult to have an
OL,17,Fopinion on it because I'm only looking
OL,18,Fat little snippets."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]wD@AOUzD@TO]
