PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784895503
OL,3,COasis reunion documentary to premiere
OL,4,Cat Venice Film Festival
OL,6,FThe Oasis reunion tour was announced
OL,7,Fin August 2024, 15 years after their
OL,8,Fdramatic split in 2009, which was
OL,9,Fprompted by a backstage brawl at the
OL,10,FRock en Seine festival in France.
OL,12,FThe band have had eight number one
OL,13,Fsingles and albums each in the UK
OL,14,Fcharts, with Wonderwall, Champagne
OL,15,FSupernova and Some Might Say among
OL,16,Ftheir most well-known hits.
OL,18,FThe Venice International Film Festival
OL,19,Fwill be held from September 2 to 12.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
